                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Book a Call</h3>
                        <p>Ready to scope an audit or want to talk through what we'd look at? Grab 30 minutes.</p>
                        <a href="https://cal.com/ateesdalejr/init" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">Schedule on Cal.com</a>
